data.description: Discover the perfect blend of community, comfort, and convenience - a place where your family's best memories are waiting to be made!Walk toward the possibilities in this excellent family home, nestled on nearly half an acre lot in the peaceful Choto area. The heart of this home lies in its generous outdoor space. Picture your family creating unforgettable memories in the expansive, level, and fenced backyard - a perfect haven for neighborhood games or peaceful relaxation, gardening or more.This gem is set in a peaceful, well-established neighborhood; and adding to the allure is access to a delightful community pool, perfect for those warm summer days.This property isn't just about the location; it's a home that has been loved and meticulously cared for by the current owners. With a desire to downsize, they are ready to pass on this haven of joy to another family. The house features a spacious three-car garage, providing ample room for vehicles and storage.Inside, you'll find a blend of comfort and elegance, with several tasteful updates that enhance the home's natural charm. The attention to detail and care in maintaining this property is evident in every corner, making it a truly move-in-ready home.We invite you to experience this wonderful property for yourself. For more information, to answer any questions, or to schedule a personal tour of this remarkable home, please don't hesitate to reach out!
